quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  3,171,JESTEBSHIRUNE BINI’METIN MINEL-LAHI WE FEDLIN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MU’UMININE
  3,172,EL-LEDHINE ESTEXHABU LILLAHI WE ER-RESULI MIN BA’DI MA ‘ESABEHUMUL-KARHU LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENU MINHUM WE ETTEKAW ‘EXHRUN ‘ADHIMUN
  3,173,EL-LEDHINE KALE LEHUMU EN-NASU ‘INNE EN-NASE KAD XHEMA’U LEKUM FAHSHEWHUM FEZADEHUM ‘IMANÆN WE KALU HESBUNALLAHU WE NI’MEL-WEKILU
  3,174,FANKALEBU BINI’METIN MINEL-LAHI WE FEDLIN LEM JEMSES/HUM SU’UN WE ETTEBA’U RIDWANEL-LAHI WEL-LAHU DHU FEDLIN ‘ADHIMIN
  3,175,‘INNEMA DHELIKUMU ESH-SHEJTANU JUHAWWIFU ‘EWLIJA’EHU FELA TEHAFUHUM WE HAFUNI ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  3,176,WE LA JEHZUNKEL-LEDHINE JUSARI’UNE FIL-KUFRI ‘INNEHUM LEN JEDURRU ELLAHE SHEJ’ÆN JURIDU ELLAHU ‘ELLA JEXH’ALE LEHUM HEDHDHÆN FIL-’AHIRETI WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  3,177,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ESHTEREWL-KUFRE BIL-’IMANI LEN JEDURRU ELLAHE SHEJ’ÆN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  3,178,WE LA JEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNEMA NUMLI LEHUM HAJRUN LI’ENFUSIHIM ‘INNEMA NUMLI LEHUM LIJEZDADU ‘ITHMÆN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  3,179,MA KANEL-LAHU LIJEDHEREL-MU’UMININE ‘ALA MA ‘ENTUM ‘ALEJHI HETTA JEMIZEL-HABITHE MINET-TEJJIBI WE MA KANEL-LAHU LIJUTLI’AKUM ‘ALEL-GAJBI WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JEXHTEBI MIN RUSULIHI MEN JESHA’U FE’AMINU BILLAHI WE RUSULIHI WE ‘IN TU’UMINU WE TETTEKU FELEKUM ‘
  3,180,WE LA JEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE JEBHALUNE BIMA ‘ATAHUMU ELLAHU MIN FEDLIHI HUWE HAJRÆN LEHUM BEL HUWE SHERRUN LEHUM SEJUTEWWEKUNE MA BEHILU BIHI JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE LILLEHI MIRATHU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  3,181,LEKAD SEMI’ALLAHU KAWLEL-LEDHINE KALU ‘INNALL-LLAHE FEKIRUN WE NEHNU ‘EGNIJA’U SENEKTUBU MA KALU WE KATLEHUMUL-’ENBIJA’E BIGAJRI HEKKIN WE NEKULU DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HERIKI
  3,182,DHALIKE BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIKUM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LEJSE BIDHELLAMIN LIL’ABIDI
  3,183,EL-LEDHINE KALU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AHIDE ‘ILEJNA ‘ELLA NU’UMINE LIRESULIN HETTA JE’TIJENA BIKURBANIN TE’KULUHU EN-NARU KUL KAD XHA’EKUM RUSULUN MIN KABLI BIL-BEJJINATI WE BIEL-LEDHI KULTUM FELIME KATELTUMUHUM ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  3,184,FE’IN KEDHDHEBUKE FEKAD KUDHDHIBE RUSULUN MIN KABLIKE XHA’U BIL-BEJJINATI WE EZ-ZUBURI WEL-KITABIL-MUNIRI
  3,185,KULLU NEFSIN DHA’IKATUL-MEWTI WE ‘INNEMA TUWEFFEWNE ‘UXHUREKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FEMEN ZUHZIHE ‘ANI EN-NARI WE ‘UDHILEL-XHENNETE FEKAD FAZE WE MAL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA ‘ILLA META’UL-GURURI